duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide compassionate care and support to patients in need of therapy.
Conduct thorough assessments of patients' mental health and well-being.
Develop personalized treatment plans to aid patients in their improvement journey.
Maintain accurate and prompt documentation of patient progress and history.
Refer patients to psychiatry services when necessary.
Collaborate with the executive team to ensure positive patient experiences and outcomes.

education_certification.credential: Graduate from an LMFT program and current license as an LMFT, LCSW, or LPCC in CA
